INSERT INTO llm_api_traces (
                prompt_id,
                model_id,
                response_data,
                status_code,
                latency_ms,
                input_tokens,
                output_tokens,
                created_at,
                request_body,
                request_method,
                request_url,
                request_headers
            ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ?, ?, ?, ?)
